# UI styling

`lang`/`dir` on **root layout only** — defaults from `src/lib/app-locale.ts`. **Logical Tailwind** (`me`/`ms`, `start`/`end`, …). **shadcn** from `src/components/ui` — default variants; compose before custom markup. Base UI: `render={<Link … />}`, not `asChild`. **`Button` / `TabsTrigger` + `Link`:** `nativeButton={false}` (app code; do not patch `src/components/ui` — update via shadcn).

English; dashboard chrome copy in `dashboard-nav-labels.ts` — no i18n unless user asks.

**Detail (Read):** [docs/agents/ui-design.md](docs/agents/ui-design.md).
